&lt;p>&lt;strong>I rarely rant on this blog. But for a change, now is the time!&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>In Swedish, there is the expression &amp;ldquo;Axelklapparklubben&amp;rdquo; which literally translates to &amp;ldquo;The Back-patting club&amp;rdquo;. It&amp;rsquo;s a mutual admiration society, an expression that is used to describe a setting where every participant is only telling each other how great they are.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>